{"content": "<h2>The Artist: Cowboy Killer</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>A sense of stillness is conveyed through how light dapples and composition directs photographed subject matter that questions our very urbane existence. The color in Cowboy Killers work is drained out of existence and what is left is a scene of apologetic paralysis. The Swedish have a word 'förlåt' which roughly translates to an expression of regret or sorrow. Joey is photo documenting the post oasis concrete peels of America overlapped with his own place in the suburban simulcrum.  <a href=\"https://app.manifold.xyz/c/all-lost\">'ALL LOST'</a> and <a href=\"https://app.manifold.xyz/c/Canalstreet-tired-cowboy-killer\">'Tired'</a> show the most recent förlåt expressions from 'C.K.', as his ardent collectors call him. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"497\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-1024x679.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-1024x679.jpg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-300x199.jpg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-768x509.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-1536x1019.jpg 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-2048x1358.jpg 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-1320x875.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/north-600x398.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>'North' A City at Midnight collection minted Sep 2022 by Cowboy Killer</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"I realized quickly after I began my teenage years that people did not think like I did. Not in a way that gave me an advantage or disadvantage, but in a way that was a catalyst for me using my perspective to explore creative outlets.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Cowboy Killer</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: Joey The Photographer</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Joy, hope and inspiration are the three human emotions that are first to be drained from the montage. The artwork titles confirm the melee. \"This Ends with Fire,\" \"We Were Never Here II,\" \"In Spite of Prayers,\" \"I Never Was,\" \"BLAME,\" \"Funeral Flowers 2,\" and \"Window Study.\" In 43 1/1 captures we see into C.K's soul and the power of expressing diminishing atrophy. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"509\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer-1024x696.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer-1024x696.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer-300x204.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer-768x522.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer-1536x1044.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer-1320x897.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer-600x408.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/Joey-The-Photographer-Cowboy-Killer.png 1798w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Joey the Photography collection minted Jan 2022</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"My Facebook from my childhood got hacked like 2 years ago and I’ve just been letting it ride.\"\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Cowboy Killer</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Palace</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Cowboy Killer composites two images here merged seamlessly through a distant haze. The Corporate world towering over our common residential dwellings. Deep simplicity the hallmark of Cowboy Killer.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"684\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-684x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-684x1024.jpg 684w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-200x300.jpg 200w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-768x1150.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-1367x2048.jpg 1367w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-1320x1977.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-600x899.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2024/11/cowboy-killer-Palace-scaled.jpg 1709w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 684px) 100vw, 684px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Palace by Cowboy Killer collected by MintFace</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/cowboy/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCowboy Killer | Line 167\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}